WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:51.759
Well, good evening, family.

00:00:51.759 --> 00:00:54.480
Thank you for joining me again today.

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:08.267
I just want to tell y'all thank you for joining us and praying with us and being here so promptly.

00:01:08.267 --> 00:01:26.569
I'm going to go over some things from what the Lord showed us in this last video, but I want to say this right off the bat: I have to apologize.

00:01:26.569 --> 00:01:29.350
I was corrected by the Spirit of the Lord today.

00:01:29.350 --> 00:01:36.460
I went about last night, some of the things I said and how I criticized President Trump, and the Lord said I dishonored him.

00:01:44.418 --> 00:01:49.644
I want to say this: I apologize for my opinion and how I present myself and some of the things I say when I criticize him.

00:01:49.644 --> 00:02:05.350
Because of things that the Lord had talked to me privately about, I brought them up publicly, and there were things that I shouldn't have said.

00:02:05.360 --> 00:02:28.423
Me and Him, we have these conversations, but what we say doesn't mean it's for the public.

00:02:28.423 --> 00:02:30.720
Does that make sense?

00:02:30.720 --> 00:02:40.171
Like my wife and I have conversations we don't bring out in public; you just have private conversations.

00:02:40.171 --> 00:02:44.040
That's the way it is with the Lord.

00:02:45.440 --> 00:02:55.109
There are certain things I said about his voting and the past that I owe apologies for, and the Lord corrected me very sternly.

00:02:55.109 --> 00:03:07.280
He said, 'Brandon, the more your platform has influence and the more it grows, you're going to be held accountable more and more for what you say.

00:03:07.280 --> 00:03:11.233
You can't just flippantly say things out of your mouth.

00:03:11.233 --> 00:03:16.542
This is a public forum; there are millions of people watching.

00:03:16.542 --> 00:03:25.351
' So, for everybody in the government, I'm going to tell you this: I apologize for how I handle myself sometimes.

00:03:25.351 --> 00:03:27.139
You know what I'm learning?

00:03:27.139 --> 00:03:32.263
I'm growing and I am immature in how I handle some things.

00:03:47.720 --> 00:03:47.940
I just want to say that I ask you to overlook certain things.

00:03:47.940 --> 00:03:50.560
I'm growing—growing pains is what I want to call it.

00:03:50.560 --> 00:03:54.354
Was that anybody else telling me to say that?

00:03:54.354 --> 00:03:57.600
No, it was the Holy Spirit.

00:03:57.600 --> 00:03:58.666
He corrected me very sternly today.

00:03:58.915 --> 00:04:03.280
I was out letting my dog go to the bathroom, and the Lord corrected me.

00:04:03.280 --> 00:04:05.680
It was a very heavy correction.

00:04:05.680 --> 00:04:15.619
So, anytime the Lord corrects me to the strength that He did today, I want to always be quick to repent and make it right.

00:04:17.379 --> 00:04:23.493
I don't even know if I could make that right other than just say, 'Listen, I was wrong.

00:04:23.493 --> 00:04:31.880
' My opinion and the conversations I have with the Father just need to—I need to learn how to filter better.

00:04:31.880 --> 00:04:39.840
So, like I said, with all that being said, I pray for grace from all y'all.

00:04:44.754 --> 00:04:44.948
There was not even anybody who said anything.

00:04:44.948 --> 00:04:47.538
It was interesting; it was just from the Lord.

00:04:50.479 --> 00:04:51.059
But I'm always quick to make it right.

00:04:51.059 --> 00:04:57.440
Be quick to repent and turn from things when the Holy Spirit corrects you.

00:05:00.330 --> 00:05:00.600
In doing so, I've continued to do that.

00:05:03.657 --> 00:05:07.439
That's why I believe that if you keep a heart right before Him, He'll keep using you.

00:05:07.439 --> 00:05:18.343
Now, praying over President Trump's decisions and the council, when I heard him talking about Taiwan and China—can you make sure what's that beeping noise in the back?

00:05:18.343 --> 00:05:19.966
It's really loud.

00:05:19.966 --> 00:05:23.280
Do you hear the beep, beep, beep?

00:05:23.280 --> 00:05:32.809
When I heard in the meeting what was being said, President Trump confirmed what we heard in the Spirit 24 hours ago.

00:05:32.809 --> 00:05:36.719
He confirmed it today in the news.

00:05:36.719 --> 00:05:44.177
It was told that Xi Jinping asked him directly—the president of China asked him directly—'Will you stand in resistance if we take Taiwan?

00:05:44.177 --> 00:05:46.280
' and President Trump would not answer.

00:05:49.470 --> 00:05:49.660
And you're about to hear that.

00:05:49.660 --> 00:05:51.013
So, what did I hear?

00:05:51.653 --> 00:05:55.795
I heard that China was going to take Taiwan as we took Cuba in the days ahead.

00:05:57.999 --> 00:06:07.567
I saw the President liberating Cuba in the days ahead, and that there would be a financial blessing over Cuba for the first time in decades.

00:06:07.567 --> 00:06:27.560
They would liberate the tyrant government that has been over them, and Rubio will slay his tens of thousands and the chameleon will slay his thousands, and there will be jealousy between the two as one rises up in the polls and people say, 'We want him.

00:06:27.560 --> 00:06:30.880
We want David as our president next.

00:06:30.880 --> 00:06:39.851
' The one will be jealous of it and he'll have his thousands, but the one will have his tens of thousands.

00:06:46.520 --> 00:06:46.810
And I saw him becoming very polished in the days ahead, Rubio.

00:06:53.240 --> 00:06:57.546
And I saw an anointing on him, and I saw Byron, the black man that has the beard—I saw that God was putting an anointing on this man.

00:07:00.119 --> 00:07:00.349
And I saw the number 25%.

00:07:15.280 --> 00:07:16.080
The Lord said, 'There are things that need to be corrected, but it's not much.

00:07:17.184 --> 00:07:20.536
I will use this man in the days ahead.

00:07:20.536 --> 00:07:26.159
' Do you know who I'm talking about?

00:07:27.816 --> 00:07:30.740
You can show his picture if you want, but I saw Byron.

00:07:30.740 --> 00:07:38.784
And the Lord said, 'I'm going to touch his life.

00:07:38.784 --> 00:07:43.559
' I saw DeSantis was 50/50.

00:07:51.942 --> 00:07:53.137
He was not as good as what he portrays, but he was a 50/50 mix.

00:08:07.702 --> 00:08:07.954
And the Lord said Rubio was not; his heart was more pliable.

00:08:29.707 --> 00:08:30.053
And He said, 'Pray for these men.

00:08:34.272 --> 00:08:34.656
I saw them becoming the cabinet of the next administration.

00:08:34.656 --> 00:08:38.468
' That's what I was praying for.

00:08:42.539 --> 00:08:42.959
I saw the African-American man.

00:08:42.959 --> 00:08:48.320
People get mad and say, 'Brandon, you say racial things.

00:08:48.320 --> 00:08:53.623
' Listen, I'm just a Southern boy.

00:08:53.623 --> 00:08:57.360
I don't know nothing about trying to be racist.

00:08:57.360 --> 00:08:59.733
I love all colors.

00:08:59.733 --> 00:09:05.710
I love blacks, whites, Chinese, Asians—I love all of you.

00:09:05.710 --> 00:09:09.519
Brandon Biggs doesn't have racism in his bones.

00:09:09.519 --> 00:09:11.348
I love you.

00:09:11.348 --> 00:09:25.440
It's because I'm trying to be politically correct, trying to talk in front of hundreds of thousands of people, and I may butcher things.

00:09:25.440 --> 00:09:30.320
Then people say, 'Well, we're not African-Americans; we're just Africans.

00:09:30.320 --> 00:09:32.490
' Well, I'm ignorant, okay?

00:09:32.490 --> 00:09:33.430
So forgive me.

00:09:33.430 --> 00:09:38.251
But I do the best I can with what I know.

00:09:39.143 --> 00:09:46.320
I saw this man rise up like a vice president in the days ahead.

00:09:47.013 --> 00:09:53.387
I saw that there would be a strong pull for him—this man right here.

00:10:11.930 --> 00:10:12.180
And the Lord said, 'Pray for him.

00:10:12.180 --> 00:10:30.764
' And that's when I was talking about the restoration and the restitution of making wrongs right for a true African-American who is going to rise up.

00:10:34.000 --> 00:10:41.040
And the Lord said, 'I'm going to restore back what the cankerworm ate.

00:10:41.040 --> 00:10:46.462
' Obama had a white mama, but he's a true black man.

00:10:55.426 --> 00:10:55.839
And the Lord said, 'Watch what I do with this man.

00:10:55.839 --> 00:10:58.840
' And I saw a blessing on him.

00:10:58.840 --> 00:11:06.460
So you pray for him because with that target on you in the spirit realm, the enemy would try to derail it.

00:11:08.560 --> 00:11:11.543
The enemy knows what's being prophesied and he doesn't want him to succeed.

00:11:26.826 --> 00:11:27.213
So we're going to pray for him.

00:11:27.213 --> 00:11:33.680
We pray for a covering over that man Byron, just like how I told you about President Trump.

00:11:33.680 --> 00:11:45.867
God has him in the office, and the enemy does not want him to fulfill what God has called him to do.

00:11:45.867 --> 00:11:56.400
There's a covering over him, and He said he must make it across the finish line.

00:11:56.400 --> 00:12:09.600
There are things that God has appointed him to accomplish that have to be accomplished, and Cuba is one of them.

00:12:15.340 --> 00:12:15.790
The Lord said, 'I'm going to liberate the people.

00:12:15.790 --> 00:12:21.851
' And I saw old grandmas praying.

00:12:21.851 --> 00:12:24.800
They had prayer shawls.

00:12:24.800 --> 00:12:28.1000
They looked like they were Catholic nuns.

00:12:39.040 --> 00:12:39.240
And they were weeping before the Lord as there was liberation coming to set the people of Cuba free.

00:12:52.215 --> 00:12:52.399
And the Lord said, 'In the days ahead, watch.

00:12:52.399 --> 00:12:55.480
Keep praying for what I'm about to do with Cuba.

00:12:55.480 --> 00:12:56.169
' Okay?

00:12:57.959 --> 00:12:59.129
And we keep bringing that up.

00:12:59.129 --> 00:13:05.832
We keep bringing it up, and I said, "It's coming.

00:13:14.720 --> 00:13:14.971
" The Lord keeps—the visions are very colorful.

00:13:21.893 --> 00:13:22.280
They're very, very vibrant.

00:13:41.070 --> 00:13:41.380
That means they're getting closer and closer.

00:13:49.456 --> 00:13:50.720
There's something about to happen.

00:13:53.080 --> 00:13:56.861
This is why the Lord keeps having us pray for this.

00:14:08.880 --> 00:14:09.200
But I saw Taiwan; I saw a two-year window.

00:14:23.300 --> 00:14:25.083
Do you remember I told you that I heard President Trump say—and I don't know if this was his thoughts, and I don't want to be invasive, but I heard it—"All we need is two years.

00:14:27.780 --> 00:14:28.120
We don't need their chips.

00:14:28.120 --> 00:14:30.600
We'll make our own chips.

00:14:30.600 --> 00:14:32.880
We will create chips in America.

00:14:32.880 --> 00:14:42.430
All we need now is two years and we will develop our own chips.

00:14:43.390 --> 00:14:46.342
" Do you have it?

00:14:46.342 --> 00:14:47.051
Yeah.

00:14:51.783 --> 00:14:52.811
I don't know if he said all that, but yeah.

00:14:52.811 --> 00:14:54.212
You said chips.

00:14:54.212 --> 00:14:55.706
"We don't need...

00:14:55.706 --> 00:14:56.453
" Yeah.

00:14:56.453 --> 00:15:01.580
Well, I didn't say it because I'm trying to be careful.

00:15:01.580 --> 00:15:02.100
Yes.

00:15:22.239 --> 00:15:22.607
So, I'm saying it today.

00:15:36.600 --> 00:15:36.940
So, I saw a two-year window.

00:15:36.940 --> 00:15:39.142
I saw a two-year window.

00:15:47.600 --> 00:15:47.840
And the Lord said, "Do they?

00:15:47.840 --> 00:15:58.971
" And so I saw why President Trump was trying to keep the dragon at bay, cracking his whip.

00:15:58.971 --> 00:15:59.725
Okay?

00:16:10.868 --> 00:16:11.131
I saw China cracking his whip.

00:16:11.131 --> 00:16:16.495
Like, "Listen," and then President Trump said, "We're 8,000 or 9,000 miles away.

00:16:16.495 --> 00:16:18.139
We're a long way.

00:16:18.139 --> 00:16:24.912
" That's why I said, "Pray for Hawaii.

00:16:24.912 --> 00:16:33.440
Pray for Hawaii because I saw a Pearl Harbor event taking place in Hawaii by China.

00:16:49.835 --> 00:16:51.430
It was Midway, a mid-ground for our bases there to go off and try to protect.

00:17:09.280 --> 00:17:15.400
So as I saw that protection there, it was a two-year window—praying over a two-year window because the Trump administration—praying over his covering over him—it has about two and a half years left.

00:17:21.110 --> 00:17:23.860
So what we would have left of what I'm seeing, what we're praying over, is China taking it, but we would have our own chips.

00:17:26.533 --> 00:17:35.226
And that was him manufacturing here in America: Texas, probably Oklahoma, whatever in the southern states where we're not crazy like some of the Democratic states are charging so many taxes.

00:17:35.226 --> 00:17:40.768
So that's what we're trying to play or not because it's a distraction.

00:17:40.768 --> 00:17:41.679
Go ahead.

00:17:41.679 --> 00:17:42.429
Well, yeah.

00:17:42.429 --> 00:17:49.459
When I see it spinning, Trump wants to pull back and he'll start to focus on this.

00:17:49.459 --> 00:17:56.284
Oh, and I see Taiwan in the midst of it.

00:17:56.284 --> 00:18:00.400
I see Taiwan in the midst of it bartering pieces.

00:18:00.400 --> 00:18:01.733
Do you understand?

00:18:01.733 --> 00:18:06.630
Trump's going to make his own chips.

00:18:06.630 --> 00:18:08.110
Do you hear?

00:18:08.110 --> 00:18:11.386
Trump's going to make his own chips.

00:18:11.386 --> 00:18:13.439
We don't need Taiwan.

00:18:13.439 --> 00:18:14.240
That's what he...

00:18:25.920 --> 00:18:26.280
and I don't mean that trying to—Chapter 2: Find scriptures to stand on—I'm just telling you what I heard.

00:18:26.280 --> 00:18:27.780
I see it.

00:18:27.780 --> 00:18:31.497
We pray for the people of Taiwan.

00:18:31.497 --> 00:18:33.783
That's what we got to do.

00:18:33.783 --> 00:18:37.280
I'm just called to fear God, not man.

00:18:37.280 --> 00:18:44.480
So I got quiet because the Lord rebuked me right there and he said, "You fear me, not them.

00:18:48.765 --> 00:18:51.829
" Because I was concerned about what Taiwan people would be saying because of what Trump had—about what he said.

00:18:54.760 --> 00:19:08.347
And so that's why I was correcting that because in my heart, I was thinking more about what they were thinking than the prophetic word of what the Lord was showing me, saying, "Trump, this is what Trump said: 'We don't need Taiwan.

00:19:08.347 --> 00:19:10.440
We have our own chips.

00:19:10.440 --> 00:19:12.853
All we need is two years.

00:19:12.853 --> 00:19:16.651
All we need is two years.

00:19:16.651 --> 00:19:20.700
'" And then I was more feeling about the people's feelings.

00:19:20.700 --> 00:19:24.079
And the Lord said, "Fear me, not them.

00:19:24.079 --> 00:19:28.354
" And he corrected me.

00:19:29.820 --> 00:19:30.120
I'm just being real.

00:19:30.120 --> 00:19:32.880
That's what was going on right there.

00:19:32.880 --> 00:19:35.000
I got rebuked again right then.

00:19:35.000 --> 00:19:39.874
So the Lord showed us more about that.

00:19:39.874 --> 00:19:45.320
Now, this is what was said about Taiwan today and President Trump just had this meeting.

00:19:45.320 --> 00:19:45.920
Go ahead.

00:19:45.920 --> 00:19:49.421
But China made clear that Taiwan is very important to them.

00:19:52.280 --> 00:19:58.959
And after your first meeting here, President Xi's spokesman put out a statement to the media saying this: "The Taiwan question is the most important issue in China-US relations.

00:19:58.959 --> 00:20:02.832
If it is handled properly, the bilateral relationship will enjoy overall stability.

00:20:02.832 --> 00:20:11.119
Otherwise, the two countries will have clashes and even conflicts, putting the entire relationship in great jeopardy.

00:20:11.119 --> 00:20:14.992
" You were still inside the meeting when that came out.

00:20:19.080 --> 00:20:19.280
That sounded almost like a threat.

00:20:32.210 --> 00:20:32.520
Was it communicated that way behind closed doors?

00:20:32.520 --> 00:20:33.140
No.

00:20:33.760 --> 00:20:34.520
And no, it wasn't.

00:20:34.520 --> 00:20:35.280
Not at all.

00:20:35.280 --> 00:20:38.731
But it has always been their most important issue.

00:20:42.600 --> 00:20:42.910
And it's not a takeover.

00:20:46.559 --> 00:20:56.697
They just don't want to see this place—we'll call it a place because nobody knows how to define it—but they don't want to see it go independent.

00:20:56.697 --> 00:21:00.777
They don't want to do it.

00:21:16.159 --> 00:21:16.319
And I think they probably would do something pretty harsh and then they would be met harshly and bad things will happen.

00:21:16.319 --> 00:21:17.440
So no, it's not that.

00:21:17.440 --> 00:21:22.560
We talked, by the way—last night we talked a whole night about that issue.

00:21:29.960 --> 00:21:31.952
I think I know more about Taiwan right now than I know about almost any country.

00:21:31.952 --> 00:21:33.247
He dominated the talk.

00:21:33.247 --> 00:21:43.706
It's always been his most important thing from the day I knew him years ago.

00:21:43.706 --> 00:21:48.000
I've known him now 11, 12 years.

00:21:48.000 --> 00:21:50.970
It's always been the biggest thing for him: Taiwan.

00:21:50.970 --> 00:21:56.217
Now with me, I don't think they'll do anything when I'm here.

00:21:56.217 --> 00:22:04.179
When I'm not here, I think they might, to be honest with you.

00:22:04.179 --> 00:22:14.400
So, I'm not sure that they do anything if it remained as is, but they have somebody there now that wants to go independent.

00:22:14.400 --> 00:22:17.579
Well, it's a risky thing when you go independent.

00:22:29.520 --> 00:22:39.893
You know, they're going independent because they want to get into a war and they want to—they figure they have the United States behind them.

00:22:39.893 --> 00:22:43.977
I'd like to see it stay the way it is.

00:22:44.365 --> 00:22:49.257
And I'll tell you something, I'll make a little news.

00:22:49.257 --> 00:23:02.360
I'd like to see everybody making chips over in Taiwan come to America because, to be honest with you, I think it's the greatest thing you can do because it's a heated situation.

00:23:02.360 --> 00:23:05.899
There's no question about it.

00:23:05.899 --> 00:23:12.960
And as you know, we have massive amounts of chip companies now from Taiwan already coming in.

00:23:12.960 --> 00:23:19.626
We expect to have 40 to 50% of the world chip business by the end of my term.

00:23:24.320 --> 00:23:24.880
And I think it should be even more than that.

00:23:24.880 --> 00:23:36.760
I think all of those chip companies—if they're smart, they're going to start heading to Arizona and the places where they're building.

00:23:36.760 --> 00:23:38.867
That's going to solve your problem.

00:23:38.867 --> 00:23:41.039
So do you see that?

00:24:32.468 --> 00:24:32.776
It's what we saw in the spirit.

00:24:32.776 --> 00:24:35.280
That was what I was seeing.

00:24:35.920 --> 00:24:54.674
And then they had the meeting and they had this interview, and this is what the Lord said: "We don't need Taiwan.

00:24:54.674 --> 00:24:56.811
" That's what he was saying.

00:24:56.811 --> 00:25:07.155
"We have our own chips.

00:25:23.520 --> 00:25:41.580
" And that was the whole reason why America was back in Taiwan.

00:25:58.080 --> 00:25:58.747
And they were moving into America.

00:26:06.880 --> 00:26:44.674
And that's why I said, "Pray for Taiwan," because I saw them being—I saw a mother hen bringing the island to her, trying to infiltrate South Korea through the politics, through North Korea, through the Philippines, through all of Japan, trying to bring them in like a mother hen.

00:26:58.739 --> 00:26:59.009
And that's why I warned you—how many times do you remember me saying this?

00:26:59.009 --> 00:27:05.039
They said, "Watch what China does.

00:27:05.919 --> 00:27:10.594
" And I saw China turning their back on the Ukraine-Russia thing that's going on.

00:27:18.719 --> 00:27:19.066
And I saw—remember I said I see a panda bear?

00:27:19.066 --> 00:27:25.520
Then I saw a turtle.

00:27:25.520 --> 00:27:28.331
I saw a dove with a wounded chest.

00:27:28.331 --> 00:27:33.669
I saw two black crows.

00:27:33.679 --> 00:27:41.039
I saw a robin, and the robin had wounded the dove.

00:28:04.540 --> 00:28:07.782
The two black crows were standing there by the dove, and they were looking at the dove that was perished on the ground with its heart ripped out.

00:28:07.782 --> 00:28:11.360
And I said this is symbolic of people.

00:28:11.360 --> 00:28:19.299
And I saw the panda turn its back upon Russia and Ukraine, and I said he was gazing towards Taiwan, and it said, "It's our time.

00:28:19.299 --> 00:28:21.679
We want to take Taiwan now.

00:28:36.000 --> 00:28:36.230
" And Xi Jinping is talking about it, and that's all they're talking about.

00:28:36.230 --> 00:28:40.106
That was three weeks ago, two weeks ago at the most.

00:28:40.106 --> 00:28:43.131
Maybe it was last week.

00:28:43.131 --> 00:28:47.979
And I said, "You're going to see an acceleration concerning Taiwan in the days ahead.

00:28:47.979 --> 00:28:48.719
Pray over Taiwan.

00:28:48.719 --> 00:28:49.039
Watch.

00:28:49.039 --> 00:28:54.354
" And now this is all they're—"Are you going to stand in our way if we do this?

00:29:10.480 --> 00:29:10.920
" Okay.

00:29:10.920 --> 00:29:26.720
But I saw as we took Cuba and liberated Cuba and made them prosperous and blessed and got rid of the government they have and set up hotels and churches and blessing.

00:29:26.720 --> 00:29:40.160
That's why we are praying for certain pastors in Miami, because they are already setting up.

00:29:40.160 --> 00:29:42.044
They're already walking by faith.

00:30:12.960 --> 00:30:13.200
They know what's coming.

00:30:13.200 --> 00:30:18.280
I've talked to them on the phone; they already know what's coming.

00:30:36.519 --> 00:30:36.779
God is about to do something huge in Cuba.

00:30:51.733 --> 00:30:52.146
So you don't wait until it happens.

00:30:52.146 --> 00:30:55.540
You're not going to be reactive; you're proactive, right?

